(11, 'FAQ', 'faq', '', '<h1>FAQ - Frequently Asked Questions</h1><p>Welcome to Wings Sportswear’s FAQ page! Here, you’ll find answers to common questions about our products, order process, policies, and more. If your query isn’t answered here, feel free to contact us directly.</p><hr><h2>1. Orders</h2><h3>1.1 How can I place an order?</h3><p>You can place an order on our website, <a rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\" href=\"https://wingssportswear.shop\">Wings Sportswear</a>. Select your desired product, choose the size or customization (if applicable), and complete the checkout process.</p><h3>1.2 What are the payment options?</h3><p>We offer two payment methods:</p><ul><li>Cash on Delivery (COD): Customers pay shipping charges online during order placement.</li><li>Full Payment: Pay the full amount, including shipping charges, online at checkout.</li></ul><h3>1.3 Can I cancel my order?</h3><ul><li>Before Dispatch: Yes, you can cancel your order by contacting us via email or phone.</li><li>After Dispatch: Orders cannot be canceled once dispatched. You may return the product after delivery if eligible under our return policy.</li></ul><hr><h2>2. Returns &amp; Refunds</h2><h3>2.1 Can I return my order?</h3><ul><li>Cash on Delivery Orders: Returns are not allowed after the delivery agent has left. Customers must check the product upon delivery and return it immediately if there is a valid reason (e.g., defect, wrong product).</li><li>Fully Paid Orders: Returns are accepted within 7 days of delivery, provided the item meets the return eligibility criteria.</li></ul><h3>2.2 What items are not eligible for return?</h3><ul><li>Customized or personalized items.</li><li>Products purchased during clearance sales, unless defective.</li><li>Items that have been altered, washed, or show signs of wear.</li></ul><h3>2.3 How do I initiate a return?</h3><p>Log into your Wings Sportswear account, navigate to My Orders, and press the Request Refund button. Fill out the form with your reason for return. Once submitted, our team will review your request and provide further instructions.</p><h3>2.4 Can I get a refund?</h3><p>Refunds are available for:</p><ul><li>Items returned in compliance with our return policy.</li><li>Orders canceled before dispatch.</li></ul><p>Shipping charges are non-refundable. Refunds will be processed based on your original payment method (e.g., online payment or bank transfer for COD orders).</p><hr><h2>3. Exchanges</h2><h3>3.1 Can I exchange a product?</h3><p>Yes, exchanges are allowed within 7 days of delivery for sizing issues or defective items. Ensure the item meets the return eligibility criteria and contact us to initiate the exchange process.</p><h3>3.2 What if the replacement item is out of stock?</h3><p>If the replacement product is out of stock, you can either choose another product of equal value or request a refund.</p><hr><h2>4. Delivery</h2><h3>4.1 How long does delivery take?</h3><p>Delivery times depend on your location. Typically, orders are delivered within 3–7 business days.</p><h3>4.2 What should I do if my order arrives damaged or defective?</h3><p>Contact us immediately with photos of the damage and your order details. We will arrange a replacement or refund at no additional cost.</p><hr><h2>5. Privacy &amp; Security</h2><h3>5.1 How is my personal information protected?</h3><p>We prioritize your privacy. Your data is securely stored and only used for order processing, shipping, and communication purposes. For more details, see our <a rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_new\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p><h3>5.2 Do you share my information with third parties?</h3><p>No, we do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except for payment processing or delivery partners.</p><hr><h2>6. Shipping Charges</h2><h3>6.1 Are shipping charges refundable?</h3><p>No, shipping charges are non-refundable, except in cases where the return is due to an error on our part (e.g., defective or incorrect item).</p><h3>6.2 Do I have to pay for return shipping?</h3><p>Yes, customers are responsible for return shipping costs unless the return is due to an error or defect on our part.</p><hr><h2>7. Custom Orders</h2><h3>7.1 Can I customize my order?</h3><p>Yes, we offer custom and personalized products. Please note that custom orders are non-returnable and non-refundable unless they arrive damaged or defective.</p><hr><h2>8. Support</h2><h3>8.1 How can I contact Wings Sportswear?</h3><p>You can reach us via:</p><ul><li>Email: <a rel=\"noopener\">hello@wingssportswear.shop</a></li><li>Phone: +8801886424141</li><li>Address: South Mugda, Mugdapara, Dhaka-1214</li></ul><p>Our support team is available to assist you with any queries or issues.</p><hr><p>Thank you for choosing Wings Sportswear! We’re here to ensure your shopping experience is smooth and satisfactory.</p>', 17, 0, 1, '2024-11-16 22:57:36', '2025-01-07 15:13:28'),
(48, 'About US', 'about-us-1', NULL, '<h3 class=\"\"><b>Wings Sportswear</b><span style=\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; background-color: var(--bs-body-bg); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight);\"><br></span></h3><p class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">License No: TRAD/DSCC/006740/2024</span></p><p class=\"\"><span style=\"background-color: var(--bs-body-bg); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\"><br></span></p><p>At Wings Sportswear, we believe in empowering athletes and fitness enthusiasts to perform at their best with high-quality sports apparel designed for comfort, durability, and style. Our mission is to combine innovative fabrics, modern designs, and cutting-edge technology to deliver gear that meets the demands of every workout, game, or adventure.</p><p>Whether you\'re hitting the gym, conquering the field, or embracing an active lifestyle, Wings Sportswear has got you covered. Our collection includes everything from performance-enhancing workout gear to everyday sports-inspired apparel, ensuring you look and feel your best wherever life takes you.</p><p>Driven by a passion for excellence and a commitment to sustainability, we source responsibly and strive to reduce our environmental footprint. At Wings Sportswear, we\'re not just a brand; we\'re your partner in pushing boundaries, reaching new heights, and achieving your goals.</p><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">Take flight with Wings Sportswear—where performance meets style!<br><br><br></p>', 1, 1, 1, '2024-11-25 15:47:16', '2025-01-07 15:13:31'),
