(51, 'Who We Are', 'who-we-are', '943c1dae-dfb9-4546-9eea-00ab475e83da.jpg', '<p>Wings Sportswear is your go-to destination for high-quality, stylish sports apparel. We offer a wide range of activewear designed for performance, comfort, and style, whether you\'re hitting the gym, the track, or the field. Our mission is to empower athletes and fitness enthusiasts with premium gear to help them perform at their best.</p>', 6, 3, 1, '2024-11-27 13:06:52', '2025-02-27 17:30:18'),
(52, 'How We Operate', 'how-we-operate', '36c810a3-df38-4a98-a664-7d9604bbd03c.jpg', '<p class=\"\">We operate with a commitment to quality and customer satisfaction. Our products are sourced from trusted manufacturers, ensuring that every piece meets our rigorous standards. We offer fast and secure shipping, easy returns, and a seamless online shopping experience to make sure you get what you need, when you need it.</p>', 10, 3, 1, '2024-11-27 13:39:35', '2025-02-27 17:46:39'),
(53, 'Why Choose Us', 'why-choose-us', 'b133601f-f3d6-4a59-a448-f33f7a6c8292.jpg', '<p class=\"\">At Wings Sportswear, we combine cutting-edge designs with top-notch materials to create sportswear that performs as hard as you do. With a focus on durability, comfort, and style, our products are crafted to fit every athlete’s needs, no matter their sport. Trust us for exceptional quality, value, and customer service.</p>', 11, 3, 1, '2024-11-27 13:40:51', '2025-02-27 17:48:57'),
